{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Survive!</h2><br>Welcome to the nightmare that is Home, a VR horror experience that breathes life into the darkest corners of West African folklore. Join the heart-pounding tale of young Efe, a boarding school student whose world has descended into a nightmarish realm. As you guide Efe through the eerie corridors, you must evade and outmanoeuvre the malevolent beings that lurk, ready to strike from the shadows.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888690/extras/otherWorldOptimized.gif?t=1732101682\" /><br><br>In Home, you play as a little girl in an environment that feels way larger to you. Forget about fighting back; your only weapon is the art of stealth. Employ your cunning, wit, and the ancient juju (magic) to evade the relentless monsters that stalk your every move. But remember, they're always watching and listening. One misstep, and their ghastly grip tightens. Find solace in the magical artefacts you uncover, for they let you see the unseen, grant you temporary shelter in the other world, and hold the key to taking advantage of the monsters' secrets.<br><br>Prepare to be engulfed by the nightmarish visuals, haunting sounds, and mind-bending puzzles of Home, a groundbreaking VR horror game rooted in the twisted tapestry of West African folklore. As the first of its kind to emerge from the depths of Africa, Home will immerse you in a world filled with dread, mystique, and unrelenting terror. Join us in this spine-tingling journey into the unknown. Wishlist it now to confront your deepest fears.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888690/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1732101682","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888690/page.bg.jpg?t=1732101682","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888690/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=173210